            "notes": "The main focus of this deck is to utilize aggressive creatures and powerful spells to quickly overwhelm the opponent in a one-on-one duel. By incorporating a mix of strong creatures like Barrowgoyf, Black Widow, and Miles Morales, along with versatile spells such as Abrupt Decay, Fatal Push, and Swords to Plowshares, the deck aims to exert early pressure and maintain control of the battlefield. Additionally, the inclusion of disruptive cards like Drannith Magistrate and Opposition Agent can hinder the opponent's strategy, giving the deck an edge in the matchup. With a solid mana base and support cards like Teferi, Time Raveler and Tamiyo, Inquisitive Student, the deck aims to outpace and outmatch the opponent for a swift victory."
